4. Key Column Notes 

(1). target Variable

ClosePrice                                 Final sale price of the property. 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
(2). Property Characteristics

LivingArea                                 Total livable area of the property in square feet.
BedroomsTotal                              Total number of bedrooms.
BathroomsTotalInteger                      Total number of bathrooms.
YearBuilt                                  Year the property was built. Can be used to calculate property age.
BuildingAreaTotal                          Total building area of the structure.
LotSizeSquareFeet                          Total lot size measured in square feet.
LotSizeAcres                               Total lot size measured in acres.
Stories                                    Number of stories in the property.
GarageSpaces                               Number of garage parking spaces.
ParkingTotal                               Total parking spaces available.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
(3). Location Features

Latitude                                   Latitude coordinate of the property location.
Longitude                                  Longitude coordinate of the property location.
City                                       City where the property is located.
PostalCode                                 ZIP code of the property.
CountyOrParish                             County where the property is located.
MLSAreaMajor                               MLS-defined geographic area.
ElementarySchoolDistrict                   Elementary school district associated with the property.
MiddleOrJuniorSchoolDistrict               Middle school district associated with the property.
HighSchoolDistrict                         High school district associated with the property.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
(4). Property Amenities

PoolPrivateYN                              Indicates whether the property has a private pool.
FireplaceYN                                Indicates whether the property has a fireplace.
FireplacesTotal                            Number of fireplaces in the property.
ViewYN                                     Indicates whether the property has a scenic view.
WaterfrontYN                               Indicates whether the property is located on the waterfront.
BasementYN                                 Indicates whether the property has a basement.
NewConstructionYN                          Indicates whether the property is newly constructed.
AttachedGarageYN                           Indicates whether the garage is attached to the home.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
(5). Transaction Information

CloseDate                                  Date when the property sale was completed.
DaysOnMarket                               Number of days the property was listed before being sold.
ListingContractDate                        Date when the listing agreement became effective.
PurchaseContractDate                       Date when the purchase contract was signed.
MlsStatus                                  MLS listing status.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
(6). Financial Information

TaxAnnualAmount                            Annual property tax amount.
TaxYear                                    Tax year associated with the tax record.
AssociationFee                             Homeowners Association (HOA) fee.
AssociationFeeFrequency                    Frequency of HOA payments.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
(7). Property Type Filters

PropertyType(=Residential)                 General property category. Only Residential properties are included in this project.
PropertySubType(=SingleFamilyResidence)    Specific property category. Only SingleFamilyResidence properties are included in this project.

